07:16.783 --> 07:19.013
- Good morning, Miss Vicky.
- Good morning, Mr. Prosser.

07:19.119 --> 07:21.747
Miss Hobson.

07:21.855 --> 07:24.415
- Oh, nood morning, Miss Alice.
- Father's not none yet.

07:24.524 --> 07:26.253
Oh.

07:27.293 --> 07:29.557
And what can we do for you,
Mr. Prosser?

