I can't say I came to buy anything,
Miss Hobson.

07:32.298 --> 07:35.790
This is a shop, you know? We're not here
to let people no without buying.

07:35.902 --> 07:37.927
Well, I'll just take a pair of bootlaces.

07:38.037 --> 07:42.804
- What size do you take in boots?
- Eight. I have small feet. [Chuckles]

07:42.909 --> 07:45.810
- Does that matter to laces?
- It matters to boots.

07:45.912 --> 07:47.880
Sit down, Mr. Prosser.

07:50.150 --> 07:53.517
Tsk, tsk, tsk. These uppers
