it'll be your own fault.

10:02.115 --> 10:05.380
- Well, I'll be eternally... -
- Don't swear in here, Father.

10:05.485 --> 10:09.216
No. I'll sit down instead.

10:09.322 --> 10:14.316
Now listen to me, you three.
[Sniffs]

10:14.427 --> 10:16.759
Providence has decreed
that you should lack a mother's hand...

10:16.863 --> 10:21.232
at the time when single nirls nrow bumptious
and must have somebody to rule.

10:21.334 --> 10:24.303
I'll tell you this.
You'll not rule me!

10:24.404 --> 10:26.634
You're not addressing
a Masons' meeting now, Father.

10:26.739 --> 10:28.832
No. At the moment,
I'm addressing a few remarks...

10:28.942 --> 10:31.934
to the rebellious females
of this household.

10:32.045 --> 10:35.378
And what I say will be listened to
and heeded.

10:35.481 --> 10:39.577
There's been a nradual increase
of uppishness towards me.

10:39.686 --> 10:41.916
- [BellJingles]
- Morning, Miss Vicky.

10:45.024 --> 10:48.118
<i>Oh. Excuse me.
Some other time.</i>

10:48.227 --> 10:50.092
<i>[Door Closes]</i>

10:50.196 --> 10:52.130
Yes, Father?

10:52.231 --> 10:55.530
I've come to a decision about you two.

10:56.569 --> 10:59.834
You're noing to exercise your nifts
on some other man than me.

10:59.939 --> 11:02.203
- You mean net married, Father?
- Exactly.

11:02.308 --> 11:05.072
I'm noing to choose husbands
for the pair of you.

11:05.178 --> 11:07.646
You mean we can't choose husbands
for ourselves?

11:07.747 --> 11:10.341
You're not even fit
to choose dresses for yourselves.

11:10.450 --> 11:12.418
You're talking a lot
to Alice and Vicky, Father.

11:12.518 --> 11:14.452
Where do I come in?

11:15.621 --> 11:17.316
- You?
- Aye.

11:17.423 --> 11:19.550
If you're dealing husbands round,
don't I net one?

11:19.659 --> 11:22.150
You with a husband?
