11:22.261 --> 11:24.161
Aye, that's a nood one.

11:24.263 --> 11:26.595
- Why not?
- Why not?

11:26.699 --> 11:28.667
Now, Mannie, I thought
you'd sense enough to know.

11:28.768 --> 11:32.864
Well, if you want brutal truth,
you're past marrying ane.

11:32.972 --> 11:35.839
- I'm 30.
- Aye. Thirty and shelved.

11:35.942 --> 11:39.309
Well, all the women
can't have husbands, Mannie.

11:39.412 --> 11:41.437
And I look to you
to take their mother's place...

11:41.547 --> 11:43.481
till I've made arrannements for them.

11:43.583 --> 11:47.485
- Dinger's at 1:00, remember.
- Dinger will be when I come in for it!

11:47.587 --> 11:50.215
- I am master here.
- [BellJingles]

11:50.323 --> 11:52.223
Oh, uh... -

11:52.325 --> 11:54.953
- Morning, Hobson.
- Morning, Mrs. Hepworth.

11:55.061 --> 11:57.529
- It's a nrand day.
- [BellJingles]

12:01.100 --> 12:03.534
Now, I've come here
