13:27.286 --> 13:30.084
Now, Mossop,
I've tried every shop in Manchester...

13:30.189 --> 13:33.420
and these are the best-made
pair of boots I've ever had.

13:33.526 --> 13:36.825
Now, you make my boots in future.
You hear that, Hobson?

13:36.929 --> 13:38.954
Of course he shall.

13:40.733 --> 13:42.633
You keep that card, Mossop.

13:42.735 --> 13:46.262
