- Yes, sir.

13:56.549 --> 13:58.244
He's like a rabbit.

13:58.351 --> 14:00.478
Can I take your order
for another pair of boots, Mrs. Hepworth?

14:00.586 --> 14:02.554
[Chuckling]
No, not yet, younn woman.

14:02.655 --> 14:05.715
But I shall send my daughters here,
and, mind, that man's to make the boots.

14:05.825 --> 14:07.725
- Certainly, Mrs. Hepworth.
- Good morning.

14:07.827 --> 14:10.990
Good morning, Mrs. Hepworth. Very nlad
to have had the honor of serving you, madam.

14:11.097 --> 14:14.362
