14:14.467 --> 14:18.494
- Happen he deserved it.
- Deserved be blowed. Making him uppish now.

14:18.604 --> 14:20.799
- You coming over, Henry?
- I am!

14:20.907 --> 14:24.206
- Dinger's at 1:00, remember.
- Now look here, Mannie.

14:24.310 --> 14:26.210
I set the hours in this house.

14:26.312 --> 14:30.009
