14:44.297 --> 14:46.322
Morning.

14:46.432 --> 14:50.334
Women think they're important
because they're boss in kitchen.

14:51.637 --> 14:52.604
Hello.

14:58.211 --> 14:59.678
Oh. Uh... -

15:10.456 --> 15:11.980
Runt.

15:13.793 --> 15:16.057
How do you do?

15:16.162 --> 15:18.357
- Frederick.
- Yes, Father?

15:18.464 --> 15:21.126
- You see where Hobson's noing?
- Yes, Father.

15:21.234 --> 15:23.896
There's a small spark of decency
in that man...

15:24.003 --> 15:28.201
that's telling him, at this very moment,
that my eye's on him.

15:33.980 --> 15:36.847
- Morning, sir.
- [Man] Ah.

15:36.949 --> 15:38.883
[Bartender]
Good morning, Mr. Hobson.

15:40.886 --> 15:42.786
Morning, Henry.

15:42.888 --> 15:45.516
- Morning, Henry.
- Up late this morning, Henry.

15:45.625 --> 15:47.593
I were detained.

15:49.762 --> 15:51.229
More.

15:51.330 --> 15:55.357
You're doing a nood class of trade, Henry.
Carriane folk now, eh?

15:58.037 --> 16:00.232
- Good health.
- I'd be in better health if it weren't for you.

16:00.339 --> 16:03.797
Do you think I pay you to dress
my daughters up like French poodles?

16:03.909 --> 16:06.377
You'll be ￡15 a year worse off for this.

16:06.479 --> 16:09.175
Now, Henry, this is not
the lannuane of friends.

16:09.282 --> 16:11.842
