16:11.951 --> 16:14.317
Aye.
[Sighs]

16:14.420 --> 16:16.718
I own I'm a bit short today.

16:16.822 --> 16:19.620
[Chuckles]
But I've cause to be and all.

16:19.725 --> 16:23.161
Sam, you've not daughters.

16:23.262 --> 16:25.355
Do yours worry you?

16:25.464 --> 16:27.398
Nay. They mostly do as I bid 'em...

16:27.500 --> 16:29.968
and missus does leatherin'
if they don't.

16:30.069 --> 16:31.969
Aye.

16:32.071 --> 16:34.699
A wife's a handy thing.

16:34.807 --> 16:39.141
- And I wish mine were still alive.
- [Chortling]

16:39.245 --> 16:43.079
I do. I know what you're thinking.
But I do.

16:43.182 --> 16:46.208
I felt nrateful
when my Mary fell on rest...

16:46.319 --> 16:49.254
