17:07.873 --> 17:11.502
I'd like my daughters to wed
temperance younn men, Denton.

17:11.609 --> 17:13.510
Good heavens.

17:13.612 --> 17:16.580
You must keep your demands
within reasonable limits, Henry.

17:16.682 --> 17:19.082
You've not three daughters
to provide husbands for.

17:19.185 --> 17:21.085
- Two, Jim. Two.
- Two?

17:21.186 --> 17:23.246
Mannie's too useful to part with.

17:23.356 --> 17:25.256
Aye.
[Chuckles]

17:25.358 --> 17:28.417
And she's a bit on ripe side
for marrying is our Mannie.

17:28.527 --> 17:30.427
[All Guffawing]

17:33.065 --> 17:36.091
Ripe? I've know 'em do it
