17:58.791 --> 18:02.227
Question is, Henry,
how high are you prepared to no?

18:02.328 --> 18:06.526
Oh, aye. I'll put me hand down
for the wedding do all right.

18:06.632 --> 18:10.068
Ah. A warm man like you
will have to do more...

18:10.169 --> 18:12.501
than pay for wedding do, Henry.

18:12.605 --> 18:14.766
What's price of an outfit, Tudsbury?

18:14.874 --> 18:17.968
Oh, I could do a milady's trousseau
for, uh, ￡60.

18:18.077 --> 18:22.571
<i>Hmm. A nd then there'll be, uh,
settlements.</i>

18:24.617 --> 18:28.610
- Settlements?
- Marriane settlements, Henry.

18:28.721 --> 18:31.053
Me pay marriane settlements?

18:31.157 --> 18:33.421
500 apiece for temperance folk.

18:33.526 --> 18:36.723
- [All Laughing]
- 500?

18:36.829 --> 18:39.525
<i>You have to bait your hook
to catch fish, Henry.</i>

18:39.632 --> 18:41.532
Then I'll none no fishing.

18:41.634 --> 18:44.899
They can stay single and lump it.
