and they're none of them bin eaters.

18:49.308 --> 18:51.208
- And their wanes.
- Wanes?

18:51.310 --> 18:55.770
Do you think I pay my own daughters wanes?
I'm not a fool.

18:55.881 --> 18:57.781
Then it's all off?

18:58.818 --> 19:03.778
From the moment you breathed the word
"settlements,"Jim, it were dead off.

19:05.458 --> 19:08.086
There'll be no marrianes in my house.

19:09.895 --> 19:12.363
[Alice Crying, Sniffling]

19:15.000 --> 19:16.968
- Father.
- Aye.

19:17.069 --> 19:20.596
No self-respecting decent man
will marry us without settlements.

19:20.706 --> 19:22.640
It's expected from a man like you.

19:22.741 --> 19:25.642
Is it? Then I'll thwart their expectations.

19:25.744 --> 19:28.838
- Father.
- Get back into shop, lot of you!

19:28.948 --> 19:30.848
[Crying]

19:34.386 --> 19:36.911
Oh, they'll soon net over it, Mannie.

19:38.624 --> 19:40.319
