you know what'll happen.

58:52.676 --> 58:56.237
Him being temperance and all.
It'll be the end of Vicky and me.

58:56.346 --> 58:59.747
- He may wake up at any moment.
- When he's like this, he'll sleep till midday...

58:59.850 --> 59:01.841
cellar or no cellar.

59:01.952 --> 59:05.752
- What are you smiling at?
- Well, in the first place, it's my wedding day.

59:05.856 --> 59:09.917
And in the second,
I think I've not an idea.

59:10.026 --> 59:12.551
- I'll be ready in a moment.
- Hmm?

59:12.662 --> 59:15.961
<i>[Bells Chiming]</i>

59:17.300 --> 59:20.667
<i>[Ship Horns Blowing]</i>

59:23.907 --> 59:25.875
<i>[Bell Tolling]</i>

59:35.452 --> 59:37.943
<i>[Tolling Continues]</i>

59:38.054 --> 59:40.989
