A lot's none on this morning.

59:41.091 --> 59:43.218
Morning, Miss Alice.
Miss Vicky.

59:43.326 --> 59:46.056
- You call them Alice and Vicky now, Will.
- [Tonether] No, he doesn't!

59:46.162 --> 59:48.392
Now listen.
You two had better net this straight.

59:48.498 --> 59:50.398
We've come to an arrannement
this morning...

59:50.500 --> 59:52.764
and if you want your Albert,
and you want your Freddy...

59:52.869 --> 59:54.769
you'll be respectful to my Willie.

59:54.871 --> 59:56.964
- Isn't that right, Albert?
- Yes, it's quite right, Alice.

59:57.073 --> 59:59.871
Good. Now you can both kiss Willie
for your brother-in-law-to-be.

59:59.976 --> 01:00:02.604
Oh, well, I... - I... - I'd as soon
not put them to the trouble.

01:00:02.712 --> 01:00:05.374
Stand still, Will.
They're making up their minds to it.

01:00:05.482 --> 01:00:08.315
- It's under protest.
- Protest, but kiss.

01:00:10.887 --> 01:00:13.151
- Good.
- It's your turn now, Vicky.

01:00:13.256 --> 01:00:15.190
You're to kiss him hearty now.

01:00:15.292 --> 01:00:17.226
- Freddy.
- Do as she says, Vicky.

01:00:19.596 --> 01:00:22.064
- Here's the ring. You're best man.
- Oh.

01:00:22.165 --> 01:00:24.099
Now no alonn.
I'll see you all inside.

01:00:24.200 --> 01:00:27.067
<i>- I want to have a word with Willie.
- [Train Engine Chugging]</i>

01:00:32.208 --> 01:00:34.108
How you feeling, lad?

01:00:34.210 --> 01:00:37.737
Me mind's made up.
I've not wrought up to point. I'm ready.

01:00:37.847 --> 01:00:39.781
It's church we're noing to,
not dentist's.

01:00:39.883 --> 01:00:42.443
