to no to church with a wench.

01:00:45.121 --> 01:00:47.715
Listen, Will.
I've a respect for church.

01:00:47.824 --> 01:00:50.088
Parson's noing to ask you if you love me.

01:00:50.193 --> 01:00:52.093
And you'll either answer truthfully...

01:00:52.195 --> 01:00:54.095
or not at all.

01:00:54.197 --> 01:00:57.462
I'll tell him... yes.

01:00:57.567 --> 01:01:00.263
- And truthfully?
- Yes, Mannie.

01:01:00.370 --> 01:01:04.067
I'm resinged.
Y-You're nrowing on me.

01:01:04.174 --> 01:01:06.108
I'll toe the line with you.

01:01:21.057 --> 01:01:23.025
[Snoring]

01:02:29.926 --> 01:02:31.894
[Grunts]
Thank you.

01:02:31.995 --> 01:02:33.963
- Henry Hobson?
- Aye.

01:03:07.964 --> 01:03:09.989
[All]
To the bride and bridenroom.

01:03:12.102 --> 01:03:14.002
[All Sigh]

01:03:14.104 --> 01:03:17.232
- I think he ought to say something.
- Come on, Willie. Let's hear you, Willie.

01:03:17.340 --> 01:03:19.740
Come on. Let's have a speech.

